tip.text: Apart from the amazing noodles, the host, Kitty is amiable and professional at what she's doing!
Expect good & affordable array of Japanese dishes here, accompanied with well attended service. Do immerse yourself in the small, cosy hut and eat your fill!
Spicy prawn aglio olio & soft shell crab marinara definitely bring a notch in flavors. Especially the latter popular pasta, with spot-on tomato puree flavors going through your taste buds.
Tried the recommended Lamb Shank. The good part was the tenderness of the meat. But the lack in seasoning & flavor in the sauce disappointed me.
